  Classes, SysUtils, Forms, Controls, Graphics, Dialogs, ExtCtrls, StdCtrls,
  laz.VirtualTrees, fgl, LCLIntf, LCLType, UWCheckBox, LCLTranslator, Spin,
  UWSystem.TextToSpeech;

